*alsa-utils-1.0.20-r6 (17 Mar 2011)

  17 Mar 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.20-r6.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.20-r5.ebuild,
  +files/sound.devices.d, -files/alsasound.initd.clip:
  Remove alsasound init script on clip, switch to new hotplug-clip-2
  device creation scheme.

*alsa-utils-1.0.20-r5 (14 Dec 2009)

  14 Dec 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.20-r5.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.17-r1.ebuild,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.11_rc2-nls.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.11_rc5-alsaconf-redirect.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.14-alsaconf-modules-update.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.17-seq.patch,
  -files/digest-alsa-utils-1.0.17-r1,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.20-init_default.patch,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.20-modprobe.d.patch:
  Bump to latest stable.

*alsa-utils-1.0.17-r1 (18 Jun 2009)

  18 Jun 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.17-r1.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.17.ebuild,
  files/alsasound.initd.clip: 
  Have the alsasound init script create devices dynamically
  based on /sys/class/sound files and a /etc/init.d/sound 
  config file. Obsoletes static devices from rm-sound-devices,
  doing what's needed in a waaay more portable fashion.

  10 Mar 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  alsa-utils-1.0.17.ebuild, files/alsasound.initd.clip:
  Add init script in CLIP core to save / restore alsa mixer settings. 

*alsa-utils-1.0.17 (09 Mar 2009)

  09 Mar 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  alsa-utils-1.0.17.ebuild:
  Initial overlay import. Fixes for dependencies. Do not install
  init script and conf files in RM.
